      "status": "confirmed",
      "description": "Apply Lorentz time dilation. Given v=0.6c (where c=1), compute gamma=1/sqrt(1-v^2/c^2) and store in particle.x. Then compute dilated time for t=10 and store in particle.y.",
      "lua_code": "function special_relativity(args)\n    local v = args.v\n    local c = 1\n    local gamma = 1 / math.sqrt(1 - v * v / c * c)\n    particle.x = gamma * v * c\n    particle.y = 10\nend",
